HEADWORD: Amassment
<hw>A*mass"ment</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OF.
<ets>amassement</ets>.]</ety> <def>An amassing; a heap collected; a
large quantity or number brought together; an accumulation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An <qex>amassment</qex> of imaginary conceptions.</q>
<rj><qau>Glanvill.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Amasthenic</ent>⟦br⟧
